text: Trigonostoma kilburni is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. The specific name kilburni is in honor of South African malacologist Richard Neil Kilburn. ==Description== ==Distribution== South Africa ==References== Category:Cancellariidae Category:Gastropods described in 2000
title: Trigonostoma kilburni
